quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  36,60,"Koo shindalakana ninanyu mbu enywe Abandu mulalaama Shetani tawe , toto ye ni Omusuku wenyu owabulafu"
  36,61,Ni mbu munaame esie ino niyo injila ingololofu
  36,62,"No khubwatoto ye yakosia omukanda omukhongo mwinywe , koo shimwaparangakhwo tawe"
  36,63,Mana ino niyo Jahanam yamwalakungwa
  36,64,Injilemwo lelo shingala mwakhayanga
  36,65,Olwa lelo khutimbia eminwa chiabu ne imikhono chiabu chiboole ninafu ne ibilenje biabu birusie obuloli khu kalia kabakholanga
  36,66,Ne khwenyanga khwakhatimbiyie tsimoni tsiabu baba nibashilanila injila halali bakhalutsi barie
  36,67,"Ne\tkhwenyanga khwakhabakalukhaniye ifwani abali hao butswa, mana shibakhanyalile okhutsia nohomba okhukalukha tawe"
  36,68,Ne wakhukofusia khumukalusinjia inyuma mubulonji mana koo shibakhaparangakhwo
  36,69,"Ne shikhwamwechesia [Muhammad] tsinyimbo tawe ne kano shikenyekhana khuye tawe, shino ni eshitsulisio nende Ikurani iretsanga abulafu"
  36,70,Khulwo khwikanyilisilia ushili omulamu ne likhuwa libure khubakhayi
  36,71,"Ko shibalolanga mbu khwabaloonjela okhurulana khumilimo chie mikhono chiefu tsisolo tsiemiruko, etsia barukanga"
  36,72,Ne nikhubanguyisilia etsindi mutsisolo etso tsiabaninangakhwo ne etsindi batsiliitsaanga
  36,73,Ne bo banyoolanga mutsisolo etso obukhonyi nende ebinywebwa kho mana shibakhupanga orio tawe
  36,74,Ne batila Abanyasaye bandi habundu wa Nyasaye mbu khobanyoole obukhoonyi
  36,75,Shibalinyala okhubakhonya halali abo nibo baliba Abasikari babu olwabali khwitsila
  36,76,"Manaamakhuwakabukalakhubelesia tawe, toto efwe khwamanya kabafisanga nende kabaretsaanga habulafu"
  36,77,Ne Omundu shalolanga mbu khwamuloonga okhurulana nende indonyande ya amatsi kolwibulo mana toto ye niye omuseeri wahabulafu
  36,78,"Ne alakhuchelasilia naye yebilila okhulongwa khukhwe -mana naboola mbu : “ ni wina oyo ulilamusia ebikumba nibimalile okhubulungukha?”"
  36,79,"Boola mbu; “ alibilamusia ulia wabiloonga olwokhuranjilila, naye ni Omumanyi muno wabuli okhuloonga khwosi”"
  36,80,Ulia wabakholela okhunyoola omulilo okhurula khumusala omubisi mana nimunyoola okhubwana omulilo okhurulana ninakwo
  36,81,Koo waloonga likulu nende eshialo shanyala okhulonga bafwana ninabo? Khulwa shina naye niye Omuloonji Omukhongo Owamachesi muno
  36,82,"Toto likhuwa lilie niyenya eshindu ashiboolela butswa mbu: “ ba’’ ni shiba"
  36,83,"Mana yatswenukha ulia wobwami bwa buli eshindu buli mumukhono kukwe, ne ewuwe niwo amulikalusibwa"
  37,1,Nditsuba khubemaanga khulunyaali
  37,2,Nende khubalia bakaninjia amabii
  37,3,Nende khubalia basoomanga obwitsulisio
  37,4,Toto Nyasaye wenyu nimulala butswa
  37,5,Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo nende ebili hakari wabio. Ne ni Nyasaye Omulesi we ebukwe tsiosi
  37,6,Toto efwe khwarona likulu liahambi khutsing’ining’ini
  37,7,Khulwokhulinda okhurulana nende buli Shetani Omukhayi
  37,8,"Balanyoola okhuwulila ebilonje bioluyali, ne baloondungwayo buli mumbeka"
  37,9,Baloondungwa ne bali nende eshinyasio shilawa
  37,10,"Halali ulia upusulanga eshindu eshititi , ne mana shimulondangakhwo eshikhupo shimesamesanga"
  37,11,Barebekhwo mbu koo abo ni baloongwa okhuloongwa okhutinyu muno okhushila ebilonje bindi biakhwaloonga? Toto efwe khwabaloonga okhurulana khuliloba litilanga
  37,12,Owukanga nabo bakholanga omubayo
  37,13,Ne nibetsulisibwa shibetsulilanga tawe
  37,14,Ne nibalola eshimanyisio nibakhola omubayo
  37,15,"Ne baboola mbu: “kano shinishiosi shiosi tawe halali ni obulosi butswa buli habulafu.”"
  37,16,"Mbunikhufwanikhumalileokhubaliloba nende ebikumba, kho toto khulilamusibwa"
  37,17,Kata bapapa befu bakhale
  37,18,"Boola mbu: “mmm! nanyu nimuli batutuyibwe .”"
  37,19,"Eyo oluyoka lulikhupwa lulala butswa, ni hawo niwo abalilola"
  37,20,"Baliboola mbu: “ abayiee, ino niyo inyanga yomurungo.”"
  37,21,Ino niyo inyanga yeyindukho yamwakhayanga